snippet.title: The Childs Sight || Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play The Childs Sight on:
-==Nintendo Switch==-
➡️ https://bit.ly/ChildsSightNS
-==Steam==-
➡️ https://bit.ly/ChildsSightST

Slowly unraveling the story of what happened to you, while lying in the crib unaware and innocent. With every minute as you explore you will remember more. Horrors will become real and clear.
Was it just fear of the unknown that haunts you or is it more?
